msgstr ""

msgid "Use HSTS"
msgstr ""

msgid "Do Not Use HSTS"
msgstr ""

msgid "Enable HTTP Strict Transport Security (HSTS)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"HTTP Strict Transport Security (HSTS) sends a header which instructs "
"browsers that the site should only be accessed over HTTPS, never HTTP. This "
"defuses an attack where an adversary gains access to your network, then "
"proxies requests through an unsecured link.\n"
"\n"
"Do not enable this option if you serve (or plan to ever serve) unsecured "
"content over plain HTTP. It is very difficult to undo this change once "
"users' browsers have accepted the setting."
msgstr ""

